Definition: a small gang of terrorist thugs claiming to seek a separate Islamic state for the Muslim minority in the Philippines
Example: uses bombing and assassination and extortion and kidnapping; In 2001 Abu Sayyaf kidnapped twenty people and beheaded one of the American captives
